haiku:
Oh, Little Tokyo
Temples, sushi and the mall
Now with GA too!

A cool place I like
It's a good place to hangout.
Must try the mezcal
Bonaventure Hotel revolving hotel bar in Downtown

i like lots of cats,
they are small, cute, fun, and fast
and they like treats too.

No one likes the valley,
Suburbs, traffic and the heat
Better have a pool!
